<h3 id="2-daisy">2. Daisy</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Daisies are also traditionally gifted to new mothers as they symbolize childbirth and motherhood[2].</li>
  <li>This makes them appropriate for congratulating new mothers and also as a gift for celebrating the maternal figures in your life on Motherâ€™s Day[2].
